Orange SA and Microsoft Corp Launch Orange TV on Xbox 360 with Kinect

Thursday, 12 Apr 2012 08:00pm EDT

Orange SA announced that together with Microsoft Corp it will launch Orange TV on Xbox 360 with Kinect: a TV experience incorporating the voice and motion recognition capabilities of Kinect for Xbox 360. The Orange TV universe will initially offer a selection of 30 channels (digital, terrestrial TV, and national channels) and channels from the Extra, Sport and Orange Cinema series packages (available to subscribers to these packages). The offer will gradually expand to include new channels, including the TV-on-demand service and the Orange Video-on-demand catalog.Â 

